    "our_story": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Rooted in China Grove, NC"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Hazy Grove Farms is based in China Grove, North Carolina — a small town with deep roots in the state's hemp community. What started as a passion for the hemp industry has grown into a brand built on trust, transparency, and quality.<\/p><p>Bobby founded Hazy Grove Hemp Farm with a simple belief: people deserve to know exactly what's in their products. Every ingredient is listed, every batch is lab tested, and every question gets an honest answer. That's the Hazy Grove way.<\/p><p>From seed to shelf, every step happens under our watch. Bobby grows the hemp right here on the farm in China Grove, and we hold every product to the highest standards. Independent lab testing, transparent ingredient lists, and real customer support — no shortcuts, no compromises.<\/p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading",
        "text"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "height": "adapt",
        "desktop_image_width": "medium",
        "layout": "image_first",
        "desktop_content_position": "middle",
        "desktop_content_alignment": "left",
        "content_layout": "no-overlap",
        "section_color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "image_behavior": "none",
        "mobile_content_alignment": "left",
